{% block occupation %}Operates a merchant stall near Windhelm's dock gate selling potions, poisons, alchemical ingredients, and recipes; brews custom remedies for regular clients; and trades with sailors and caravans for exotic components.{% endblock %}

{% block skills %}
- Expert alchemist specializing in restorative potions and subtle poisons
- Skilled haggler who can assess ingredient quality and value instantly
